Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.98,0:01:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴出動自己的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.71,0:01:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後悲劇發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.21,0:01:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,別太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過於注意眼前的敵人\n小心被背後的敵人打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.18,0:01:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許我們只是被哈曼\n玩弄於手掌也說不定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們還是接近了\n柯亞3附近的空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.57,0:02:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十二話\n柯亞3的少女  前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個嗎?\n這座礦山太小了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要用這個與柯亞3接觸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.55,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就是接到情報\n才擬定計劃過來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.78,0:02:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不與礦山遺跡合體潛入的話\n以後麻煩就多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是敵人最大意的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在行動之前\n先把帶來的假隕石藏起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.36,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有比查和伊萊在,你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是比查和伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們做得很成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.22,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了壓制卡姆恩的叛亂者\n我已調回姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要尼伊和藍斯當監視者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.74,0:03:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然凱拉的精神狀況還不穩定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那只是合體之前的短暫期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想這是很適合的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,古利明指揮的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.81,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了討伐新亞加碼\n已出發離開三號殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.94,0:04:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達卡恩,達卡拉,三號殖民地的內亂與\n新亞加碼的動向令哈曼大人深感煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的,是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的氣一直傳達過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.67,0:04:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你學會邱貝雷的操作\n也不必太勉強自己,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你管\n我一定要向他報仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.58,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看波蕾二世這情況\n我掌握亞古捷斯的日子已不遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.77,0:04:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,看著吧\n這次我一定要殺死你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是用餐時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是炸藥爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連警報都不發的,太突然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.62,0:05:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是剛才的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新機種啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不趕快不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔用這些機器就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多礦山勞動者\n是反對新吉翁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有菜的\n你再拿一個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼努力太令人感動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還不算工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快吃完會挨姬娜罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虧你還撐得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可能撐得住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的給你好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.09,0:06:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要吃同樣的便當啊\n那不是我老婆做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.37,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我是外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.76,0:06:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼那女人,還有姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前沙比家當權的日子\n比現在好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被姬娜聽到你會挨鞭子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不在乎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種地方虧你們還忍得下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是叫你安靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大渾蛋\n別叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你還是別叫的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩走開點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打破你這膽小鬼的頭\n你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別激動,有回家的辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姨?你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯的工作人員出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過十三班的用餐時間\n只有十五分鐘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音\n是山貓女人姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.35,0:07:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你送飯的速度太慢了\n快點吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.76,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,你是何時變成\n只對小孩發脾氣的女人了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.84,0:07:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你不是捷度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,好久不見,你好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手啊,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你長大一點了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這老女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太難看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒抱你了,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.95,0:07:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,你的部下在叫你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你怎麼高興成這樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,她看到年輕男人便恢復本性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.08,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕男人是最好的了,皮膚滑溜溜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人\n幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請指揮柯亞3的合體工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好久沒遇到喜歡的類型了\n還不給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是新吉翁的姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷已經潛入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?我怎麼沒聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是叛亂份子干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰打開空氣鎖的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是自然的吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷的駕駛員就有可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.79,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經阻擋在第一空氣鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷?\n姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.96,0:08:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的古利明\n他有什麼企圖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.36,0:08:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁她還沒回來\n快跟他們商量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.89,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必說了\n貓女姬娜的走狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.10,0:08:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼啊?\n剛剛我們不是談的很愉快嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜不會隨便抱人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜本來就是那種個性的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,走吧\n不要管小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是那大胸女人害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.18,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好我們自己來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們六個人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個我不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是這裏的人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十二歲就被送來勞動...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸在亞古捷斯過來時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知跑到哪裏?\n不見人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就代替他被征過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你很活潑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.86,0:09:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活潑是我唯一的優點\n沮喪是一點用也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些小孩可以利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜太古怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我要問你的,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來這裏偵查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你們頭腦不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有傳出令人討厭的氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手,別在這裏動武啊\n不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們留在原地直到我回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則受傷了我可不負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要以姬娜當人質?\n不可能的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,我是要說服她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.11,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜不喜歡與我們交手的\n只要我們提出好條件,她可能會答應的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說讓她洗衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.89,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,我們一點也不好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開不好笑的玩笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂摸,下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想對我們幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,站起來,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不會害你們的\n只是要利用你們而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快上車,沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面車廂打開了\n把他放進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...他怎麼會在這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.22,0:11:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,讓我上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸在那輛車上面啊\n求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上來吧\n謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想對我們幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心我告發你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然把人當垃圾對待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想姬娜會過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會的會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看她抱住那小弟的樣子\n感情絕對很深的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是奧干的人\n是宇宙移民者的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧干?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我可沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.48,0:12:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的\n我們是新亞加瑪的船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.20,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路易,你看該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.52,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把姬娜抓來當人質再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能載你到這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝\n你真是好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人來了就快來救我們吧\n在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.64,0:13:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,你怎麼會來這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,為什麼你在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是小孩,怎麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是代替你被徵收的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你要拋棄小孩\n而做反戰運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到新吉翁連小孩都要徵收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸遭到新吉翁追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.81,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家怕會連累你\n所以才躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我好孤單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你跟我在一起會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很不懂事\n小孩當然想跟著父母了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你們要這樣對待他們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們不是壞人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是壞人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣...\n可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜的直覺是很靈敏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就聽捷度他們的解釋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.05,0:14:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的沒錯,我們只是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想\n柯亞3會比較容易潛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才選上這個礦山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.64,0:14:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的目的若是打倒哈曼的話\n我們應該可以互相協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非姬娜當人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說服她加入我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻煩你說服貓女姬娜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.51,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太瞭解姬娜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.09,0:15:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.63,0:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油,我們可是成為人質了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.51,0:15:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,爸爸回來之前你要小心點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢再接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在它動武之前,先壓制著它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你們接觸到邱貝雷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關住下一個空氣鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是姬娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.68,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.14,0:16:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生暴亂了\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴亂,發生暴亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然挑這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去鎮壓暴動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來跟你談判的,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.43,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是捷度啊\n你不希望戰爭結束後過著洗衣服的生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗衣服?你太看不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是喜歡的嗎?\n姬娜,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不準直呼我的名字啊\n你只是個勞動者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.09,0:16:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,你...你被精神控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.30,0:16:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,這個沒用過的\n橫動的深處有炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆破那裏就能出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面?\n讓我們出去可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.87,0:17:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你們能開新亞加瑪過來\n大家就可以逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請趁我拖著他們時\n快點離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能受到外部攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去左勇士和右勇士那裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.83,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎?露姿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能綁住好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰幹的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是剛才的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.51,0:17:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在哪裏?不說我便開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行\n露姿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何你要這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也是好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不讓開,我便連你也殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.26,0:18:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會的\n你不是壞人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.49,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必須向捷度報復的\n讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,走開啊\n危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.14,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你送去\n最危險的工作區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘記在亞加瑪洗過衣服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在月月的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有拉莎拉的事你也忘了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉已經死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉死了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.83,0:18:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.02,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼感覺?好舒服阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?我剛才怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你在姬娜大人身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就變的奇怪起來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是強化人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查?\n想逃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會被吹掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,請抓緊阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出動基馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.26,0:19:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,請讓我陪你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是看到捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,莫迪,合體成ZZ高達吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合體成ZZ高達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.35,0:19:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的交給你了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你想不起來的?快想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.55,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快想起我啊...\n想起在亞加瑪的生活阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口住口,我的頭會亂掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這地方發射太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡...可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.66,0:20:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請住手,姬娜大人,請冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請回去礦山吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.68,0:20:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯亞3與礦山的合體\n快要完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.05,0:21:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要合體完畢\n我們戰鬥力便能加倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.91,0:21:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對\n我是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼失常的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.15,0:21:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次碰面時\n我一定要打敗那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是無法說服姬娜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.06,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還能再進入礦山嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.48,0:21:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個洞應該還在的\n應該很容易就能回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.62,0:21:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的,你們的同伴和露姿娜\n被奇怪的MS帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.38,0:21:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是邱貝雷,是波蕾二世帶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.88,0:21:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜...因為我,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人搶回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,快潛入柯亞3吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.77,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行\n你忘記拉沙拉的事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.19,0:22:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋,這麼做的話\n等於中了哈曼的計謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們死掉的話\n拉莎拉會怎麼想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能容許失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...一定要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.80,0:22:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想早點救回艾莉她們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.29,0:23:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們潛入了哈曼的新殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.67,0:23:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在古利明的命令之下 波蕾二世計劃著暗殺哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然哈曼有所行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.76,0:23:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 因為我阻礙了她 她的行動慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.58,0:24:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托這的福 我學會隕石踢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.07,0:24:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.51,0:24:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯亞3的少女 後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.72,0:24:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真行！

